<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قال الشخ الألباني:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>صحيح - <span class="c2">((الصحيحة)</span>) <span class="c2">(٥٩٣)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
